<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 29 Apr 2026 01:50:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>山姆·班克曼-弗里德重新审判的动议被美国法官驳回</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/sam-bankman-fried-s-motion-for-new-trial-rejected-by-us-judge</link><description>一名联邦法官驳回了 FTX 联合创始人 Sam Bankman-Fried 提出的自行动议，要求根据这位前加密货币之王声称的新证据进行新的审判。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV5O8v7917bU/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 21:23:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/sam-bankman-fried-s-motion-for-new-trial-rejected-by-us-judge</guid></item><item><title>最新 DeFi 黑客事件动摇信心，以太坊面临十字路口</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-28/ether-eth-faces-a-crossroad-as-defi-hacks-shake-confidence</link><description>第二大加密货币的价值越来越依赖于其上构建的一切的弹性。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i6Ftz9vspNJU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 21:00:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-28/ether-eth-faces-a-crossroad-as-defi-hacks-shake-confidence</guid></item><item><title>摩根大通任命前高盛高管领导区块链部门</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/jpmorgan-taps-former-goldman-executive-to-lead-blockchain-unit</link><description>摩根大通 (JPMorgan Chase &amp;amp; Co.) 已任命前高盛集团 (Goldman Sachs Group Inc.) 高管奥利弗·哈里斯 (Oliver Harris) 领导其区块链部门 Kinexys，该银行希望扩大使用加密基础技术构建的产品和服务的采用。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iSrOiB_ha8Co/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 16:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/jpmorgan-taps-former-goldman-executive-to-lead-blockchain-unit</guid></item><item><title>Polymarket 寻求 CFTC 批准将主要交易所带回美国</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/polymarket-seeks-cftc-blessing-to-bring-main-exchange-back-to-us</link><description>据知情人士透露，Polymarket 正在采取措施，试图将其主要交易所带回美国，通过允许美国人访问该平台，可能会为已经快速增长的行业带来动力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/icGoU2A7ktAs/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 15:03:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/polymarket-seeks-cftc-blessing-to-bring-main-exchange-back-to-us</guid></item><item><title>Novogratz 表示比特币重夺 10 万美元将很困难</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</link><description>亿万富翁 Michael Novogratz 表示，在当前的宏观经济环境下，以市场领头羊比特币交易价格再次超过 10 万美元来衡量，加密货币领域的广泛复苏可能会很困难。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iikdUX6WTmck/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 28 Apr 2026 12:20:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-28/novogratz-s-galaxy-digital-posts-loss-as-crypto-rout-lingers</guid></item><item><title>交易员权衡伊朗问题进展，比特币触及 12 周新高</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/bitcoin-reaches-12-week-high-on-iran-deal-optimism</link><description>比特币触及 12 周高点，然后小幅回落，因为交易员消化了有关美伊谈判结束中东冲突进展的相互矛盾的迹象。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/in7uHlRB8Zek/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 04:02:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/bitcoin-reaches-12-week-high-on-iran-deal-optimism</guid></item><item><title>100 亿美元挤兑后 DeFi 救援伤害反华尔街宣传</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/defi-rescue-hurts-anti-wall-street-pitch-after-10-billion-run</link><description>去中心化金融正处于其历史上最大规模的协调救援之中，这一努力的特点是道德风险担忧和临时谈判，这与该行业作为传统金融颠覆者的创始宣传格格不入。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iMX1bkovgeE0/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 18:13:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/defi-rescue-hurts-anti-wall-street-pitch-after-10-billion-run</guid></item><item><title>战略放缓比特币购买，转向普通销售</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/strategy-slows-bitcoin-buying-switches-back-to-common-sales</link><description>Strategy Inc. 在过去 7 天购买了 2.55 亿美元的比特币，在过去两周花费了 35 亿美元之后，放慢了购买数字货币的步伐。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iV72m45pZHwE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:24:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-27/strategy-slows-bitcoin-buying-switches-back-to-common-sales</guid></item></channel></rss>